WEBVTT

00:00.154 --> 00:06.154
Subs by Zhalom and Raceman
www.forom.com

00:07.155 --> 00:09.478
My name is Melinda Gordon.

00:09.773 --> 00:12.359
I'm married,
I live in a small town,

00:13.502 --> 00:15.216
and I own
an antique shop.

00:15.241 --> 00:17.205
I might be just like you.

00:17.235 --> 00:21.623
Except that from the time I was a little
girl, I knew that I could talk to the dead.

00:22.591 --> 00:25.581
Earthbound spirits,
my grandmother called them.

00:26.211 --> 00:28.683
They're stuck here because they have
unfinished business with the living

00:28.718 --> 00:31.091
and they come to me
for help.

00:34.025 --> 00:39.263
In order to tell you my
story, I have to tell you theirs.

00:40.932 --> 00:42.837
<i>Previously
on ghost whisperer...</i>

00:42.837 --> 00:45.233
there's a plane in the air...

00:45.256 --> 00:47.533
no one is flying it!

00:51.495 --> 00:54.812
Yeah, I really don't get the feeling
that he was on that flight.

00:54.818 --> 00:55.562
I mean, what are the chances?

00:55.595 --> 00:57.542
I can't lose
my brother, melinda.

00:58.896 --> 01:01.962
- Wait!
- They're mine.

01:09.698 --> 01:13.431
I've been trying to work up
the courage to go in there,

01:14.147 --> 01:16.581
- look at the passenger list.
- Andrea...

01:16.596 --> 01:18.601
there's
something I have to tell you.

01:18.635 --> 01:20.630
- You saw mitch.
- Andrea--

01:20.637 --> 01:24.393
- Don't! No. No.
- But I'm not sure--

01:24.395 --> 01:26.392
no way.
It's not him.

01:26.408 --> 01:28.501
It was 250 people, jim.

01:28.747 --> 01:30.763
Do I really have
the right to ignore that?

01:30.767 --> 01:34.041
What about the thousands people
you could help the rest of your life?

01:34.046 --> 01:36.693
You can't trick those souls
into staying here.

01:36.696 --> 01:40.780
I will release
all your precious souls.

01:40.817 --> 01:44.550
And in return,
I'll take...you.

01:44.965 --> 01:47.251
Mitch!

01:52.587 --> 01:56.003
- Mitch?
- I'm so sorry, Mitch.

01:56.006 --> 01:58.142
I was supposed
to be on that plane, Melinda,

01:58.148 --> 02:00.140
I can't believe Andrea
it's dead.

02:00.648 --> 02:01.941
How'd it happen?

02:01.947 --> 02:05.720
She was driving
to your apartment in the city.

02:06.498 --> 02:08.911
She tried so hard
to reach you.

02:09.407 --> 02:12.501
I guess her car got caught in the
path of the plane.

02:12.505 --> 02:15.973
- Do you think she suffered?
- No.

02:19.306 --> 02:21.561
No, I don't think so.

02:21.718 --> 02:23.911
This can't be happening!

02:27.778 --> 02:30.831
she's mine!

